  "text": "As performance tests for the code we have chosen the challenging Noh spherical shock problem (Noh 1987 ) and [CITATION_1] point explosion problem. Analytical solutions exist in both cases. A perfect gas equation of state with (γ = 5/3) has been used for these tests. We will also present calculations for Cepheid model pulsations with a realistic equation of state and opacities to show the application of the code to stellar oscillations. ",
